{"tid":1169063,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士埋站疑阻路　DC9閘車示威　兩度落車「問候」","createTime":"2019-05-24T06:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T02:24:13.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2f94147d916d2155e0c0d3161f04d499105b98c2","tid":1169063,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"巴士埋站疑阻路 的士閘車示威 兩度落車「問候」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WnhaNd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WnhaNd&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=33fc5db4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WnhaNd</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190524/photo/bkn-20190524133032865-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190524140955\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190524133032865-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190524140955&h=7a4ef6ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全感受到司機的怒火。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周四（23日）上午10時46分，在域多利道近西寧街交界，有巴士疑埋站時凸出半個車身，引起尾隨的士不滿。<br />\n<br />\n待巴士徐徐離站時，的士隨即切雙白線爬頭，在巴士前急停，的士司機落車怒罵︰「X你老母呀，你老母臭X，隔籬唔X攞埋啲，一定隊你」，巴士車長亦不甘示弱：「你過嚟呀，你切雙白呀」。其後的士駛離路段，事件看似告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n豈料巴士沿域多利道行駛時，兩車又狹路相逢，的士司機再次落車，向車長指手畫腳喝罵，惟車長已不予理會。"},{"pid":"24ed261b149923457ea65977dc3c2c09c408e522","tid":1169063,"uid":135896,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"任何情況之下,閘人車 好似 已經一定係 危險駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bde7b42a4160ae4b438d9358ffb8d99ac026101","tid":1169063,"uid":153863,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"24ed261b149923457ea65977dc3c2c09c408e522","tid":1169063,"uid":135896,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"任何情況之下,閘人車 好似 已經一定係 危險駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /